notes.text:
This module deletes a contact from its existing TAG ID and adds it to a new TAG ID. 

NOTE: This module needs to be attached to the main TAG ID Module in order for it to perform its job.

This module deletes a contact from its existing Group and adds it to a new Group  using a Group ID. 

NOTE: This module needs to be attached to the main Group Module in order for it to perform its job.
This Module is limited to selecting contacts only with a specific GROUP ID
This Module Is limited to selecting contacts only with a specific TAG ID
This module Generally selects contacts from CIVICRM
